   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00091"/>Herrn Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav
                  Schwarzkopf</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207296">Tiefer Graben 23</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00092"/><date>29. 6. 905</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb21647">Paul Marx</rs></hi> möchte Ihnen für <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb333602" subtype="implied"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb31491">Juden</rs>karten</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chicken; und we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> Ihnen der Tag <hi rend="underline" n="1">nicht</hi>
               componirt, bitte ihm ins <rs type="org" ref="#pmb36430">Deut<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che Volkstheater</rs>
               brieflich abzuwinken.</p><p>Den Schlu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s des namenlosen <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04064-1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29903" subtype="implied">Stückes</rs> hab ich geändert<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04064-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="Cf" target="1905-06-29"/>.</note>, <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s kein Men<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch mehr den <unclear><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29983">Mei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ter</rs></unclear> ahnen wird. In der Hoffnung da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Sie von die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>em Doppel<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>inn i<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>erlich keinen Gebrauch mache<unclear>n</unclear></p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
